Key Lessons From This Task
Always use the required command style
Installation → apt
Service control → service
Jenkins version determines Java requirement
Jenkins 2.492.x → Java 17 works
Jenkins 2.568.x → Java 21 required
The lab validator checks Jenkins objects, not just files
User email must exist in the Jenkins user profile.
Editing XML alone may not always satisfy validation.
For Jenkins startup issues
Always check:
service jenkins status

then:

cat /var/log/jenkins/jenkins.log

This workflow is the correct approach for future xFusionCorp/KodeKloud Jenkins installation tasks.
